  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge, Cast\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nThe cli crate is becoming quite huge and contains two bins that use the same deps.\r\n\r\nWe made an effort to structure the `cmds` module by bin, we should consider taking this a step further and moving some functionalities to different crates.\r\n\r\neither extend the existing `forge` and `cast` crates or something like `forge-cli` and `cast-cli`.\r\n\r\nIn any case, we definitely need a `common` crate that provides types used by both, we also need this to make anvil a standalone cli. (`EvmOpts` type for example)\r\n\r\nSo I'd start there. and then we can gradually split things off.\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\nRef #857\r\n\r\n_No response_",
